  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2418820/extras/16ef5f31a6ef0cbe5b22f91c0ff7a111.poster.avif?t=1701314439\" width=800 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2418820/extras/16ef5f31a6ef0cbe5b22f91c0ff7a111.webm?t=1701314439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>The game has three story branches: normal, realistic, and mystical walk.<br>In the normal branch you can just walk around the summer city, the forest and the spring.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2418820/extras/c8ca78ad9c6aa6f8338c339059edab96.webp?t=1701314439\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2418820/extras/c8ca78ad9c6aa6f8338c339059edab96.poster.avif?t=1701314439\" class=\"bb_img\" width=640 height=480 /></picture></span><br>In the realistic branch be careful, the map is flooded with blood, there are 9 scary endings and foul language. Pay attention to the red eyes - these are the endings.<br>Choose your path and unlock all the endings. You can move with the map to different locations. The game has an abandoned camp, a river, a summer town, a forest, a spring. There are 11 endings in the mystical branch and 9 in the realistic one.<br><br>The girl took her camera and went for a walk on a sunny August day. It's only up to you to decide how it will turn out - whether it will be an ordinary walk to an abandoned camp, or she will meet a terrible end.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2418820/extras/99d804d29a51acbb1bdb0e9165158725.poster.avif?t=1701314439\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2418820/extras/99d804d29a51acbb1bdb0e9165158725.webm?t=1701314439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Features:<br>- pleasant graphics;<br>- simple controls;<br>- interesting gameplay;",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2418820/extras/16ef5f31a6ef0cbe5b22f91c0ff7a111.poster.avif?t=1701314439\" width=800 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2418820/extras/16ef5f31a6ef0cbe5b22f91c0ff7a111.webm?t=1701314439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>The game has three story branches: normal, realistic, and mystical walk.<br>In the normal branch you can just walk around the summer city, the forest and the spring.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2418820/extras/c8ca78ad9c6aa6f8338c339059edab96.webp?t=1701314439\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2418820/extras/c8ca78ad9c6aa6f8338c339059edab96.poster.avif?t=1701314439\" class=\"bb_img\" width=640 height=480 /></picture></span><br>In the realistic branch be careful, the map is flooded with blood, there are 9 scary endings and foul language. Pay attention to the red eyes - these are the endings.<br>Choose your path and unlock all the endings. You can move with the map to different locations. The game has an abandoned camp, a river, a summer town, a forest, a spring. There are 11 endings in the mystical branch and 9 in the realistic one.<br><br>The girl took her camera and went for a walk on a sunny August day. It's only up to you to decide how it will turn out - whether it will be an ordinary walk to an abandoned camp, or she will meet a terrible end.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2418820/extras/99d804d29a51acbb1bdb0e9165158725.poster.avif?t=1701314439\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2418820/extras/99d804d29a51acbb1bdb0e9165158725.webm?t=1701314439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Features:<br>- pleasant graphics;<br>- simple controls;<br>- interesting gameplay;",
